The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for automatic classification of Alzheimer's Disease using medical imaging data. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) as well as machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact of the algorithm on healthcare (cs.HC).
